## âœ… `.gitattributes`

```gitattributes
# Normalize text files to LF (Unix-style line endings)
* text=auto eol=lf

# Treat Python and Markdown files as text
*.py text
*.md text

# Treat images and icons as binary
*.png binary
*.ico binary
*.icns binary
*.tiff binary
*.jpg binary

# Prevent VSCode config or compiled cache from being misclassified
.vscode/* text
__pycache__/* text